I am a CM fan... of about the first 5 seasons. After that it goes downhill into formulaic writing and outrageous plots. By season 7 or 8 I found myself wondering why I was even still watching, though occasionally there was a gem of an episode that kept me hopeful. However they really seemed to run out of ideas and fell back on gore and shock to create interest most of the time. This show should have quit while it was ahead, and left on a high note. The actors did well with what they had though. Not their fault, more so the writers. I cared about the main characters thanks to the acting, but i just got so sick of the pervert-of-the-week theme that I gave up watching. Sadly.
